# 🏋️‍♂️ Gym Management System

🚀 A modern **Gym Management Web Application** built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript** featuring smooth animations, interactive UI, and a gaming-inspired experience.

---

## 🔥 Overview

This project is designed to manage gym activities in a simple, interactive, and visually appealing way.
It combines **clean UI**, **dynamic functionality**, and **gaming vibes 🎮** to create a unique user experience.

---

## ✨ Features

* 🔐 User Login & Signup System
* 🏋️ Workout Tracking Interface
* 📊 Progress Monitoring (UI-based)
* 🎮 Gaming-style animations and effects
* 💻 Fully responsive design
* ⚡ Smooth transitions & interactive UI
* 🧠 User-friendly navigation

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* 🌐 **HTML5** – Structure
* 🎨 **CSS3** – Styling & Animations
* ⚙️ **JavaScript (App.js)** – Logic & Functionality

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```
Gym-Management-System/
│── index.html
│── style.css
│── app.js
│── assets/
│   ├── images/
│   ├── icons/
```

---

## ⚡ Installation & Setup

1. Clone the repository

```
git clone https://github.com/your-username/gym-management-system.git
```

2. Open the project folder

3. Run the project

```
Open index.html in your browser
```

